Please update http://rainbrurpg.sourceforge.net/wiki/bin/view/Main/BuildingFromSources when modifying this file.

The following package should be installed before RainbruRPG is installed:

* Boost.Program_options 1.42
  + homepage:
    http://boost.org
  + download:
    http::/sourceforge.net/projects/boost/files/

* Boost.Format 1.42
  + homepage:
    http://boost.org
  + download:
    http::/sourceforge.net/projects/boost/files/


* qt4-ruby
  + homepage: 
    http://rubyforge.org/projects/korundum/
  + download:
    http://rubyforge.org/projects/korundum/
